---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'

const lang = 'en' as const

const lineUrl = 'https://line.me/R/ti/p/@twmedpro'
const waUrl = 'https://wa.me/886900000000'
const mailUrl = 'mailto:info@colanclinic.com'

const tiers = [
  {
    label: 'Tier 0 · Pain Medicine Private Consultation',
    items: 'Private appointment including consultation and single-zone ultrasound assessment. Additional zone +NT$500.',
    fee: 'From NT$800',
    desc: 'Pain Medicine private consultations are by reservation. Consultations are unhurried, with real-time ultrasound assessment as standard.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Tier 1 · Foundation Injection Therapy',
    items: 'Ultrasound-guided injection, prolotherapy, acupotomy, intra-articular hyaluronic acid',
    fee: 'NT$1,500–$6,500 (TBC)',
    desc: 'Suitable for first-time regenerative medicine patients, mild to moderate injury, or chronic pain. Priced by treatment site and number of injections.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Tier 2 · Blood-Based & Vascular Therapy',
    items: 'PRP, SportVis, TAME',
    fee: 'NT$12,000–$30,000 (TBC)',
    desc: 'Autologous blood or vascular intervention therapies. Suitable for moderate to severe injury, tendon degeneration, and chronic joint pain.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Tier 3 · Cell Regeneration Therapy',
    items: 'BMAC, Amniotic Matrix',
    fee: 'NT$25,000–$75,000 (TBC)',
    desc: 'Advanced regenerative options for severe degeneration, treatment-resistant pain, or cases where PRP has shown limited effect.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Tier 4 · Combination Procedures',
    items: 'Custom combination therapy, PRP + localized autologous fat injection (with SVF)',
    fee: 'From NT$70,000 / by assessment (TBC)',
    desc: 'For complex or multi-site conditions. A personalized treatment plan is designed by your doctor after assessment.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Tier 5 · Neuromodulation Therapy',
    items: 'Nerve hydrodissection (with B12), botulinum toxin',
    fee: 'NT$1,500–$25,000+ (TBC)',
    desc: 'For nerve compression, chronic neuropathic pain, and muscle spasm-related conditions.',
  },
]
---

<Layout
  lang={lang}
  pathname="pricing"
  title="Treatment Fee Reference｜Colan Clinic・Luzhou Pain Medicine"
  description="Self-pay treatment fees at Colan Clinic, including ultrasound-guided injections, PRP, BMAC, TAME, nerve hydrodissection, and regenerative medicine procedures."
>
  <section class="fv-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="fv-eyebrow">Self-pay Treatment Fees</p>
      <h1>Treatment Fee Reference</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p>The following outlines our self-pay treatment fee tiers. All fees are explained clearly by your doctor before any treatment begins. Actual costs depend on the treatment site, procedure complexity, and materials used. The ranges below are for reference.</p>
      <div class="fv-notice">
        <strong>⚠️ Note:</strong> The fees below are pre-opening reference ranges. Official pricing will be announced before the clinic opens. Feel free to ask via LINE if you have questions.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Fee Tiers</h2>
      {tiers.map((tier) => (
        <div class="fv-tier">
          <div class="fv-tier-head">
            <span class="fv-tier-label">{tier.label}</span>
            <span class="fv-tier-fee">{tier.fee}</span>
          </div>
          <p class="fv-tier-items">{tier.items}</p>
          <p class="fv-tier-desc">{tier.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Payment & Fee Notes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>All fees are explained in full before treatment. Procedures only proceed with your consent.</li>
        <li>Registration and consultation fees are cash only.</li>
        <li>Private treatment procedures accept cash (NTD) and major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard).</li>
        <li>For pre-paid multi-session packages, unused sessions are refundable upon request.</li>
        <li>Any fee changes will be announced in advance.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Treatment Fees & Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>The treatment response to regenerative medicine procedures — including but not limited to PRP, BMAC, and TAME — is subject to individual variation based on factors such as personal constitution, extent of injury, lifestyle, and post-treatment compliance. As these treatments involve inducing biological responses within the body, recovery progress and degree of improvement differ between patients. The clinic is unable to guarantee specific outcomes or identical results.</p>
      <p>Once a treatment has been performed, the associated fees are non-refundable in principle, as they encompass physician assessment, medical procedures, consumable materials, and related medical services.</p>
      <p>In cases where an adverse outcome is attributable to a clinical error by the clinic, or where a confirmed consumable quality issue is identified, the clinic will arrange a repeat procedure, corrective treatment, or other appropriate remedial measures at no additional charge. For pre-paid multi-session packages, sessions not yet performed may be eligible for a refund in accordance with the Consumer Protection Act of the Republic of China and applicable regulations.</p>
      <p>Prior to treatment, the physician will provide a thorough explanation covering indications, expected outcomes, potential risks, alternative treatment options, and an itemised breakdown of fees. Treatment will only proceed after the patient has fully understood and explicitly consented. This clinic does not engage in any form of coercive or high-pressure sales practices.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Fee Inquiries</h2>
      <div class="fv-cta-row">
        <a href={lineUrl} class="fv-cta fv-cta-line" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LINE Consultation</a>
        <a href={waUrl} class="fv-cta fv-cta-wa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
        <a href={mailUrl} class="fv-cta fv-cta-mail">Email Us</a>
        <a href={`/${lang}/first-visit/`} class="fv-cta fv-cta-ghost">First Visit Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
